  "steps": [
    "Heat ghee in a non-stick pan, add water chestnut flour, mix and sauté on medium heat for 10-12 minutes or till the mixture turns brown and fragrant.",
    "Add sugar and 1½ cups hot water and mix till no lumps remain.  Cook for 4-5 minutes.",
    "Add milk, mix well and cook for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add green cardamom powder and mix well.",
    "Add cashewnuts, pistachios and almonds and mix well",
    "Transfer into a serving bowl, sprinkle cashewnuts, pistachios and almonds and serve immediately."
